Fear!

All players current Zoinks are converted into chips at the begining of the round.
    *Big D's Shop of Horrors does not accept chips.

Each player is also given 5 chips ontop of whatever they had.

Player play 5 hands of Texas Holdem, Gambling with their chips. Each player must antee every round.

The team who ends the 5 rounds with the most chips wins and recives 5 Zoinks per player. If the teams are tied continue playing until a winning team is decided.

At the end of the game all players chips are converted back into Zoinks!